PURIFICATION DOESN'T WORK

99
00:10:01,266 --> 00:10:04,436
I wanted to work in the film industry.

100
00:10:04,436 --> 00:10:08,770
I got a job with a film studio
prop department.

101
00:10:09,108 --> 00:10:13,477
But there was a gap between
my ideals and reality.

102
00:10:13,712 --> 00:10:18,172
The salary wasn't much and the work was hard.

103
00:10:27,459 --> 00:10:32,260
Take that cigarette out of your mouth.

104
00:10:32,998 --> 00:10:36,525
No one uses this crap nowadays.

105
00:10:36,969 --> 00:10:39,563
That's not the point!

106
00:10:43,575 --> 00:10:45,177
I'll wash it.

107
00:10:45,177 --> 00:10:50,444
A prop is an actor's tool.

108
00:10:52,317 --> 00:10:57,890
Each dress and prop has their own spirit.

109
00:10:57,890 --> 00:11:03,462
So...you have to take good care of them.

110
00:11:03,462 --> 00:11:04,895
I understand.

111
00:11:08,100 --> 00:11:11,160
You'd better quit soon, too.

112
00:11:16,942 --> 00:11:18,375
Is that...

113
00:11:21,313 --> 00:11:23,713
Get rid of it.

114
00:11:38,664 --> 00:11:40,632
