115
00:11:40,632 --> 00:11:45,070
The noise was from the shelf
where blood-stained armor lay.

116
00:11:45,070 --> 00:11:47,163
Mr. Tadano.

117
00:11:54,780 --> 00:11:57,044
Mr. Tadano.

118
00:12:10,395 --> 00:12:12,158
Who are you?

119
00:12:23,175 --> 00:12:26,445
Actor fatality on film set.

120
00:12:26,445 --> 00:12:29,214
Was it this man?

121
00:12:29,214 --> 00:12:31,614
I didn't see his face.

122
00:12:32,017 --> 00:12:37,148
The budget was tight but they were ambitious.

123
00:12:37,356 --> 00:12:40,883
The film industry was on a decline.

124
00:12:40,926 --> 00:12:44,763
They were slacking.

125
00:12:44,763 --> 00:12:48,167
They didn't pay out wages.

126
00:12:48,167 --> 00:12:51,432
