128
00:12:54,907 --> 00:12:57,676
All the armor was left on set.

129
00:12:57,676 --> 00:12:59,211
Was that blood?

130
00:12:59,211 --> 00:13:06,208
The device under his armor went off too soon.

131
00:13:06,852 --> 00:13:10,481
He was still a young actor.

132
00:13:12,524 --> 00:13:16,392
If only I were there.

133
00:13:17,596 --> 00:13:19,531
I can't regret enough.

134
00:13:19,531 --> 00:13:22,568
We must do a purification ceremony.

135
00:13:22,568 --> 00:13:25,799
We've done it many times.

136
00:13:26,939 --> 00:13:34,573
But...despite the ceremony and prayers,

137
00:13:36,114 --> 00:13:42,144
The spirits wouldn't budge.

138
00:13:47,893 --> 00:13:52,592
The props have souls.

139
00:13:54,666 --> 00:13:56,930
What are you going to do?

140
00:13:57,836 --> 00:13:59,004
Are you going to quit, too?

141
00:13:59,004 --> 00:14:01,340
No.

142
00:14:01,340 --> 00:14:04,366
I like films.

143
00:14:04,776 --> 00:14:07,613
I won't quit. No matter what.

144
00:14:07,613 --> 00:14:10,173
Ok.

145
00:14:13,986 --> 00:14:16,216
Right.

146
00:14:27,933 --> 00:14:33,572
